node.text: YouTube fam! We hit 25k subs!! We’re gonna pick one random subscriber, fly you and a friend to LA to workout with me and the crew @zooculture, and sit in on a podcast of your choice (FATKZ, KATS, BTB, Calabasas Fight Companion) All submissions must be sent to Thicccfans@thicccboy.com. The winner will be announced next week! We will be picking another winner next at 50k so make sure you subscribe to get a chance to come rock with the crew! All winners must be subscribed to the Thiccc Boy YouTube Channel!
